title: Is Catherine Elizabeth Clennan’s GoFundMe Campaign Authentic?
subtitle: Social media users mocked what appeared to be a sincere (if tone-deaf) GoFundMe plea from Catherine Clennan, but the campaign resembled a publicity hoax.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: A woman named Catherine Elizabeth Clennan is genuinely seeking several million dollars via GoFundMe to live her dream life.
